data.description:
Nice solid ranch offers 3-4 bedrooms, 2 baths, 1 car attached garage, mud room, 1st fl laundry room, beautiful sunroom that could be a 4th bedroom, an small office space and a partially finished basement...all this on a nice level lot on a cul-de-sac thats close to all amenities. This home needs some TLC and it is priced accordingly...it will not go FHA or VA financing. 
Turn this 2,000+/- sq ft ranch into your new home today...
